content: It got the password for the vimeo livestream, but no login data for the Zoom meeting. Is that right?

I also only got the password for the Vimeo livestream, but I emailed the organisers and they forwarded me an email with the Zoom link. I think attendees were supposed to receive the Zoom link, but maybe not everyone did?

Hi Martin,

In fact we sent you the info email on the 27th (I just checked!)... Maybe it has been put into your Spam folder. However, I have re-sent it right now, please check!

Thanks a lot! Unfortunately I didn't get a new mail (also no mail on the 27th), and my spam folder is empty. Just to double check, the adress is either brandenburg [at] uni-muenster.de or the gmail adress I used for registering.
aha! You registered with a gmail address... I am sending a new mail to the other address.
